Hair Transformation Vlog ✨🔥
From grown-out to glossy dimensional magic! Here’s a step-by-step breakdown of my full hair refresh using all @wella haircare + colour 🌟👇
Save for your next appointment 🫶
Step 1: Lightening
We started by lightening using Wella Blondor Plex 9, carefully foiled and hand-painted each section for max brightness + blend.

Step 2: Rinse + Prep
Once processed, we rinsed and treated the hair with Wella Post Colour Treatment to lock in the colour and protect the hair.

Step 3: Toner Magic
We zone-toned using a mix of:
✨ Roots: Colour Touch 4/71 + 5/3
✨ Mid-lengths: Illumina 6/19 + 8/13
✨ Ends: Colour Touch 88/07 + 8/3

Step 4: Cleanse + Repair
After toner processing, we rinsed and washed with Wella Ultimate Repair Shampoo & Conditioner, followed by a spritz of Ultimate Repair Leave-In before brushing.

Step 5: The Cut
Added soft, long face-framing layers to elevate the shape 💇‍♀️

Step 6: Style & Protect
Finished with Wella Thermal Image Heat Protectant and styled to perfection!💁‍♀️✨

This transformation is giving glossy, dimensional brunette with a luxe lived-in vibe 💫 #hairstyle #vlog #hairvlog #haircolor
